THE PERMANENT READER

The Omar Reader is someone who constantly feels:

"There must be something deeper than what people usually notice."

They naturally question appearances.

They dislike shallow explanations.

They enjoy discovering hidden systems behind ordinary life.

Curiosity is not a hobby.

It is part of their personality.

